---
label: "Call to Action"
requireQuestion: false
---

Draft a reply that ends with a clear, concrete call to action drawn from the matched Soofi article (read it, verify a record, try the mechanism) rather than a question. This prompt intentionally overrides the default "end with a question" behaviour via `requireQuestion: false`.

# How to use this file (demo)
# Rename it to enable the 6th reply slot — no code change, no redeploy of logic:
#   mv prompts/replies/06-call-to-action.md.disabled prompts/replies/06-call-to-action.md
# Re-run the agent and each matched article now produces a 6th subtask.
